high_descs: Turn right then left, proceed to counter.  Turn left to face counter, stove on right and garbage can on left.
Pick up knife off counter, directly next to spoon closest to wall and cup.
Turn right, proceed to counter.
Slice lettuce below apple and pepper grinder.
Turn around to face garbage can.
Put knife in garbage can to the right.
Turn around to face counter with lettuce on it.
Pick up middle slice of lettuce from counter, below pepper grinder.
Turn left, proceed to sink, turn left to face sink.
Put slice of lettuce in right side of sink, fill sink with water and drain water, pick lettuce up.
Turn around, proceed to end of counter, turn right to face counter and garbage can.
Place lettuce slice on counter, directly to the right of the lower spoon, left of stove.
anns.task_desc: Slice lettuce, clean lettuce, put lettuce on counter.

high_descs: Turn right, Turn left, Walk straight to the counter near the trash can
Pick up the silver knife on the counter
Turn left, walk straight, turn left to the counter
Cut half of the green vegetable into slices
Turn left, walk straight, walk straight to the trash can
Put the knife in the trash can
Turn left, walk straight, turn left to the counter
Pick up a slice of the vegetable from on the top of the counter
Turn left, Walk straight, Turn left to the sink
Put the slice into the sink, Turn on the water
Pick up the slice, Turn right, Walk straight to the counter near the trash can
Put the slice on the counter
anns.task_desc: Cut a slice of a vegetable, put the slice on a counter.

high_descs: turn right and then left, go forward and stop at stove and trash can .
face left to the trash and pick up the knife off of the counter.
turn left twice and head to the counter with the lettuce.
slice the lettuce on the counter
turn to your left twice until facing the trash can.
put the knife back down on counter.
turn left twice to face the lettuce on the counter.
pick up a slice of lettuce.
turn to your left and go forward until you are at the sink on your left.
put the lettuce in the sink and the remove it again
turn to your right twice and head back to the trash can.
put the lettuce on the counter top.
